rComments: Incredible TA! Very helpful and kind. One of the best I ever had.
He was my TA for PHL271, I came for the hotness, and stayed for the clarification on course material. He's awesome.

My experience in Alex's class exemplifies the benefits of having a TA who is both gorgeous and brilliant:). His outgoing and friendly nature, as well as his genuine desire to help his students made his tutorials helpful and fun. With a *great* body and a mind to match, Alex is an undeniably amazing TA :).His students are truly lucky to have him.
